Module java.base
Package java.lang

Class Void

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Void
  • public final class Void
extends Object
    The Void class is an uninstantiable placeholder class to hold a reference to the Class object representing the Java keyword void.
    Since:
    1.1
